        <mxCell id="note" value="Writes always target the Region 1 primary; a primary loss means promoting a replica (RPO = replication lag). Single writer = no conflict handling.&lt;br&gt;AWS: Aurora read replicas / Global Database; Cosmos DB with a single write region." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;fontSize=10;fontStyle=0;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="150" y="545" width="720" height="40" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
